Table
Description
areas
area codes (e.g., ZIP, State)
commodities
commodity codes (e.g., UNSPSC, HS)
tax_rates
tax rate records per area × commodity code
tax_jurisdictions
mapping area code → tax zone or jurisdiction
tax_lookup (optional)
hierarchical lookup like CSV example to handle commodity rollups



Lookup flow:
	1. Identify area by code (ZIP or state).
	2. Find exact or hierarchical commodity code match.
	3. Retrieve applicable rate.

